2009-02-06  Stefan Kost  <ensonic@users.sf.net>

	* bdk-pixbuf/bdk-pixbuf.sgml:
	* bdk/bdk-docs.sgml:
	* btk/btk-docs.sgml:
	* libbail-util/bail-libbail-util-docs.sgml:
	  Add online urls for library.bunny.org. This allows other docs to do
          btkdoc-rebase --online --html-dir=html
          before publishing docs and have working xrefs.
          Whitespece cleanup for bdk/bdk-docs.sgml.

