2002-01-06  Havoc Pennington  <hp@pobox.com>

	* btk/btk-docs.sgml: remove btk- prefix from TreeView and a few
	other entities, more consistent anyway (I thought this would make
	links to "BtkTreeView" etc. go to the ref page, not the struct,
	but it wasn't the problem, the issue is the way btkdoc-mkdb
	decides what's an object, see CheckIsObject() routine)

