	* btk/tmpl/btkarg.sgml: new sections from
	David Benson <daveb@idealab.com>.

	* btk/tmpl/btkvbox.sgml: 
	* btk/tmpl/btkhbox.sgml: fixed line endings.

	* btk/tmpl/btkvbbox.sgml: update from Lee Mallabone
	<lee0@callnetuk.com>

	* bdk/tmpl/drawing.sgml: fixed error in bdk_draw_arc() @angle2 param
	- it is relative to @angle1 rather than from the 3 o'clock position.

	* btk/tmpl/btkfontseldlg.sgml: changed enums to use @ fields.

	* btk/tmpl/btkcolorsel.sgml: 
	* btk/tmpl/btkcolorseldlg.sgml: 
	* btk/tmpl/btkprogress.sgml: 
	* btk/tmpl/btkprogressbar.sgml: new sections from Tom Martone
	<tom@martoneconsulting.com>

	* btk/tmpl/btkclist.sgml: partially written documentation from
	Paul Schifferer <isengard@geocities.com> who won't be able to finish it

