Thu Aug 19 14:43:08 1999  Owen Taylor  <otaylor@redhat.com>

	* bdk/tmpl/gcs.sgml bdk/bdk-sections.txt: Added section. 
	  (Written a while ago but fell through the cracks)

	* btk/btk-docs.sgml: Add a &hash; entity here as a
	  temporary hack. (There is no standard entity
	  for '#', and no way of escaping '#' in btk-doc)

	* btk/tmpl/btkrc.sgml: Use the above to fix up #rrggbb
	  string literals.

